    <h2>From $300/month cubicle to $30M/year company</h2>
    <h3>And our impact is growing even faster than we are!</h3>

    <div class="large-text space-bottom">

        <p>We signed our first client in 2007 while sitting at a rented desk in San Francisco. Since then, we’ve grown to become a well-capitalized business with $30M in annual revenue serving 37 utilities—including 7 of America’s 10 largest. Our product innovations now reach nearly 5 million homes. </p>

        <p>Together with our clients and their customers, we’re saving energy, saving them money, and directly helping to reduce global carbon emissions. And our positive impact increases every single day. </p>
    
    </div>
    
