    <h4><span class="highlight">OPOWER Today</h4>
        
    <p>OPOWER is a 100-person-strong, all-star team of software developers, engineers, and sales, marketing, and operations experts. From our home base near Washington, D.C., we’ve been growing by leaps and bounds, and we’ve just opened a new office in San Francisco to help us continue to do that. We’re doubling the total amount of energy we’re helping North Americans save at home every six months: by the end of 2010, the amount of energy we’ll have saved will equal a third of the energy produced by entire US solar industry—and we’re having a great time doing it! We’re a company that’s deeply committed to transparency and to our staff, and we were built with collaboration, collective success, and quality of life for all in mind. </p>

